<subSubSection id="18481CB81DDF9B5337F6C578BC991ADE" pageId="15" pageNumber="34" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="C8A758F84D26E7D189C0EF92AA4EAAF7" pageId="15" pageNumber="34">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2374C7A459DCDF5BB00A908C75F7DAE0" pageId="15" pageNumber="34">Body piceous with green brassy reflections. Elytral surface smooth, striae reduced to basal third, impunctate, 4 setiferous punctures on interval 3, stria 2 absent. Profemur glabrous. Abdominal sternum VII with 5+5 setiferous punctures.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
